pr_body:
Add relation extraction component for English and Russian to DeepPavlov (Google Summer of Code 2021 Project).

- Model is created based on the ATLOP model ([paper](https://arxiv.org/pdf/2010.11304.pdf), [git](https://github.com/wzhouad/ATLOP)).
- English Dataset: DocRED ([paper](https://www.aclweb.org/anthology/P19-1074/), [git](https://github.com/thunlp/DocRED))
- Russian Dataset: RuRED ([paper](http://www.dialog-21.ru/media/5093/gordeevdiplusetal-031.pdf), [git](https://github.com/InstituteForIndustrialEconomics/rured))


More details in [Gist page](https://gist.github.com/anasedova/0cdcf8588f73873c5d7c4998cec90b37).

pr_body:
Add relation extraction component for English and Russian to DeepPavlov (Google Summer of Code 2021 Project).

- Model is created based on the ATLOP model ([paper](https://arxiv.org/pdf/2010.11304.pdf), [git](https://github.com/wzhouad/ATLOP)).
- English Dataset: DocRED ([paper](https://www.aclweb.org/anthology/P19-1074/), [git](https://github.com/thunlp/DocRED))
- Russian Dataset: RuRED ([paper](http://www.dialog-21.ru/media/5093/gordeevdiplusetal-031.pdf), [git](https://github.com/InstituteForIndustrialEconomics/rured))


More details in [Gist page](https://gist.github.com/anasedova/0cdcf8588f73873c5d7c4998cec90b37).

pr_body:
Add relation extraction component for English and Russian to DeepPavlov (Google Summer of Code 2021 Project).

- Model is created based on the ATLOP model ([paper](https://arxiv.org/pdf/2010.11304.pdf), [git](https://github.com/wzhouad/ATLOP)).
- English Dataset: DocRED ([paper](https://www.aclweb.org/anthology/P19-1074/), [git](https://github.com/thunlp/DocRED))
- Russian Dataset: RuRED ([paper](http://www.dialog-21.ru/media/5093/gordeevdiplusetal-031.pdf), [git](https://github.com/InstituteForIndustrialEconomics/rured))


More details in [Gist page](https://gist.github.com/anasedova/0cdcf8588f73873c5d7c4998cec90b37).
